data.description: Welcome to your dream home located on the north end of Zanesville! This charming ranch-style house, perfect for those who appreciate minimalistic living and easy maintenance, is waiting for you to make it your own. Featuring 2 cozy bedrooms, 1 bathroom, and a convenient one-car garage, this home is designed for comfort and ease. Enjoy the privacy on the covered back porch, and benefit from additional storage space with a handy extra shed. Fresh updates include a new roof, and new siding, along with many other improvements throughout the home. Situated on a nice, flat city lot, this property combines the best of peaceful living with the convenience of city life and being close to all amenities. Don't miss out on making this beautiful house your new home. Call today to schedule your private showing! Let’s turn this house into your home...
